mapproperties.key: // obtain attached elemetns System.out.println(getAgentID() + " executing -> " + getID() + ":" + getType()); Hashtable<String, mired.ucm.grid.TypesElement> devices; try { devices = eaSMClient.getControllableDevices(); for (String device : devices.keySet()) { mired.ucm.remote.orders.RemoteBatteryOrder batteryCharge = new mired.ucm.remote.orders.RemoteBatteryOrder( device, 10000); mired.ucm.remote.orders.RemoteBatteryOrder batteryDischarge = new mired.ucm.remote.orders.RemoteBatteryOrder( "Battery_31", 0); if (devices.get(device) == mired.ucm.grid.TypesElement.BATTERY) { if (eaSMClient.getBatteryEnergy(device) <= 10000 && mired.ucm.Utils.noOrderXAfterLastY( eiOrdersHistory.getHistory(), batteryDischarge, batteryCharge) && !mired.ucm.Utils.thereExistsXWithinYMillis( eiOrdersHistory.getHistory(), batteryCharge, 60 * 60 * 1000)) { System.out.println(getAgentID() + " charging"); // Charges the battery eaSMClient.sendOrder(batteryCharge); eiOrdersHistory .getHistory() .add(new mired.ucm.Pair<Long, mired.ucm.remote.orders.RemoteOrder>( eaSMClient.getSimTime(), batteryCharge)); System.out.println("sending switch on order to " + device); } else { if (eaSMClient.getBatteryEnergy(device) > 10000 && !mired.ucm.Utils.thereExistsXWithinYMillis( eiOrdersHistory.getHistory(), batteryDischarge, 60 * 60 * 1000)) { System.out.println(getAgentID() + " charging"); // Charges the battery eaSMClient.sendOrder(batteryDischarge); eiOrdersHistory .getHistory() .add(new mired.ucm.Pair<Long, mired.ucm.remote.orders.RemoteOrder>( eaSMClient.getSimTime(), batteryDischarge)); System.out.println("sending switch on order to " + device); } } } } } catch (java.rmi.RemoteException e) { // TODO Auto-generated catch block e.printStackTrace(); } eaSMClient.tryItAgainAfter(10);
// REPLACE THIS COMMENT WITH YOUR CODE System.out.println(getAgentID() + " executing -> " + getID() + ":" + getType());
